com.cube.storm.ui.view

Enum View

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<View>
      • com.cube.storm.ui.view.View
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<View>

    public enum View
extends Enum<View>
    This is the enum class with the list of all supported view types, their model classes and their corresponding view holder class. This list should not be modified or overridden
